[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_0001090
name: Root internal radius
def: "The inner radius of a plant's root. It is an important factor in plant growth and development, affecting the plant's ability to absorb water and nutrients from the soil." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Sep 25 2025)
