[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_0001838
name: Argon diffusivity
def: "The rate at which argon molecules or atoms move through gaseous or aqueous media due to concentration gradients and molecular motion. This parameter is used as a conservative tracer for studying gas transport processes in terrestrial and aquatic systems." []
