[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000299
name: Series type
def: "A categorical descriptor specifying whether a data series represents temporal measurements, replicates, treatment variations, or other organizational structures. This classification enables proper interpretation of data relationships and appropriate statistical analysis methods in experimental datasets." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
