[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000300
name: Time series
def: "A sequence of observations or measurements recorded at regular or irregular time intervals, allowing analysis of temporal trends, patterns, and dynamics. Time series data is fundamental for understanding process evolution, forecasting, and identifying periodic or long-term changes in environmental, biological, and physical systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000004
is_a: bervo:BERVO_8000232 ! Concept
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Attribute http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
