property_value: bervo:BERVO_measured_in http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000302
name: Condition
def: "A descriptive statement specifying the particular set of environmental, chemical, biological, or physical circumstances under which an experiment or observation occurs. Conditions define the parameters being tested and are essential for interpreting results and enabling comparative analysis across different experimental treatments." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000006
