property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000303
name: Method
def: "A detailed description of the procedures, protocols, techniques, and instrumental approaches employed to collect data or conduct measurements. Methods documentation ensures experimental transparency, reproducibility, and allows other researchers to critically evaluate the validity and applicability of findings." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000007
