property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000304
name: Algorithm parameter
def: "A configurable input value or setting that controls the behavior and performance of a computational algorithm. Algorithm parameters include thresholds, weighting factors, iteration limits, and other tunable variables that significantly influence data processing outcomes and result interpretation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000008
