property_value: bervo:BERVO_measured_in http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000305
name: Comment
def: "Textual notes or annotations providing context, clarification, or additional information about experimental data, methods, or results. Comments serve as informal metadata that can document unexpected observations, data quality concerns, or interpretive insights that enhance understanding of research findings." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000011
