property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000306
name: Instrument
def: "The analytical or measurement device employed to collect data, including specifications such as make, model, serial number, and calibration information. Instrument selection critically influences measurement accuracy, precision, and comparability across studies, making detailed documentation essential for data quality assessment and method standardization." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000012
