property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000309
name: Mathematical context
def: "Descriptive information regarding mathematical operations, transformations, or analytical frameworks applied to data. This includes information about scaling approaches, normalization procedures, and mathematical conventions used in data processing and interpretation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000018
