property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000310
name: Relative
def: "A descriptive specification indicating the reference state, baseline, or comparative standard against which a measurement is expressed. This provides essential context for interpreting values that represent changes, differences, or ratios relative to a defined reference condition." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000020
