property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000311
name: Chemical context
def: "Information describing the chemical environment, reaction conditions, molecular interactions, or the role of specific molecules within chemical processes or experimental systems. Chemical context includes reaction type, substrate role, product formation, and chemical mechanistic information." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000026
