property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000312
name: Molecule
def: "A specification of chemical identity when molecular composition or structure varies as a dimension in experiments or datasets. This concept enables tracking of chemical diversity in reaction systems, metabolic pathways, or multi-component analyses where different molecules are analyzed or compared." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000027
