property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000313
name: Reaction
def: "A description of a chemical or biochemical transformation specifying reactants, products, reaction conditions, and mechanistic information. Reaction descriptions enable understanding of stoichiometry, energy requirements, and biological or environmental significance of chemical processes." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000028
