property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000314
name: Surface type
def: "A categorical description of the physical surface on which interactions, reactions, or adsorption processes occur, such as mineral surfaces, organic matter, biofilm matrices, or interface boundaries. Surface type critically influences reaction rates, mass transport, and binding affinities in environmental and biological systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000029
