property_value: bervo:BERVO_measured_in http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000315
name: Bead type
def: "A specification of the material composition and surface properties of beads used in laboratory experiments such as soil homogenization, grinding, or chemical extraction procedures. Bead type selection affects contamination risk, extraction efficiency, and final sample composition in geochemical and biogeochemical analyses." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000030
