property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000319
name: Wavelength
def: "The distance between successive peaks or troughs of electromagnetic radiation, determining the energy and spectral characteristics of light. Wavelength specifications are critical for spectroscopy, photometry, and light-dependent processes such as photosynthesis and phototaxis in environmental and biological studies." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
