[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000324
name: Taxon
def: "The taxonomic classification of an organism at various hierarchical levels including species, genus, family, or higher ranks. Taxon designation enables biological identification, comparative analysis, and linking of experimental data to phylogenetic and ecological frameworks." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000045
