property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000325
name: Media
def: "The nutrient-containing liquid, semi-solid, or solid preparation used to culture microorganisms or cells. Media selection influences organism growth, metabolic activity, and community structure in laboratory experiments and is critical for replicability and standardization of microbial research." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
