[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000326
name: Media composition
def: "A specification of the chemical constituents, nutrient elements, and trace components comprising growth media. Media composition documentation enables reproducibility and understanding of how nutrient availability and chemical environment influence organism growth and metabolism." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
