property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000327
name: Media addition
def: "Amendments or supplements added to culture media such as vitamins, growth factors, chelating agents, or specialized compounds. Media additions enable targeted modification of growth conditions and selective cultivation of organisms with specific nutritional or physiological requirements." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
