[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000333
name: Protein
def: "A functional macromolecule composed of amino acids that catalyzes reactions, provides structural support, and regulates cellular processes. Protein characterization and quantification are fundamental for understanding enzyme activity, metabolic capacity, and biochemical function in organisms and environmental systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
