property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000334
name: KEGG subsystem
def: "A functional classification system from the KEGG database that groups genes and proteins involved in specific metabolic or signaling pathways. KEGG subsystem annotations enable systematic analysis of organism metabolic capabilities and prediction of functional roles in biogeochemical cycling." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
