property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000340
name: Taxonomic level
def: "The hierarchical rank within the Linnaean classification system (kingdom, phylum, class, order, family, genus, species) at which an organism is identified. Taxonomic level specification determines the resolution and precision of biological classification and affects interpretation of biodiversity and community composition." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000090
