property_value: bervo:BERVO_measurement_of http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA
property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000341
name: Strain change effect
def: "The observable phenotypic or functional consequence resulting from genetic modification, strain substitution, or evolutionary changes in a microbial population. Strain change effects provide insights into genotype-phenotype relationships and the adaptive significance of genetic variations in experimental and environmental contexts." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000092
