property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000343
name: Environmental parameter
def: "A measurable property of the physical, chemical, or biological environment such as temperature, pH, moisture content, or nutrient concentration. Environmental parameters characterize the conditions influencing organism function and biogeochemical processes in natural and managed ecosystems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000103
