property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000345
name: Read type
def: "The categorization of sequencing reads based on their origin (single-end vs. paired-end) and structural characteristics (full-length, 16S, metagenome, transcriptome). Read type specification is essential for appropriate bioinformatic processing and interpretation of molecular data." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000112
