property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000347
name: Measurement
def: "A quantitative or qualitative determination of a physical, chemical, or biological property using established protocols and calibrated instruments. Measurement accuracy and precision are fundamental to data quality and scientific reproducibility across all empirical research." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000120
