property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000350
name: Size
def: "The physical dimension or scale of an object, organism, or particle measured in linear units (length, width, height, diameter). Size measurements are fundamental for characterizing physical properties, particle distributions, and organism morphology in biogeochemical studies." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
