property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000352
name: Expression level
def: "The quantitative measure of gene or protein abundance in a cell, tissue, or organism reflecting the activity of genetic regulation. Expression level measurements are essential for understanding functional gene activity, metabolic capacity, and stress responses in biogeochemical contexts." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
