property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000354
name: Fitness score
def: "A quantitative measure of organism survival, reproduction, or competitiveness relative to wild-type or reference strains. Fitness scores enable assessment of genetic variants' ecological and physiological consequences in laboratory and environmental contexts." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
