property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000355
name: Genetic interaction score
def: "A quantitative measure of synergistic or antagonistic effects between two genetic mutations or perturbations beyond their individual contributions. Genetic interaction scores reveal epistatic relationships and functional interdependencies between genes in complex biological systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
