property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000356
name: Stoichiometric ratio
def: "The proportional relationship between reactants or products in chemical or biochemical reactions based on molecular formulas. Stoichiometric ratios are fundamental for calculating reaction yields, energy requirements, and elemental cycling rates in biogeochemical models." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
