property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000358
name: Presence
def: "A Boolean property indicating the occurrence or detection of a substance, organism, genetic element, or phenotype in a sample or environment. Presence data enables community composition analysis and tracking of specific organisms or traits across samples." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
synonym: "extant" EXACT []
