property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000359
name: Essentiality
def: "A Boolean property indicating whether a gene, protein, or metabolic function is required for organism survival under specified conditions. Essentiality assessments reveal functionally critical genes and identify metabolic bottlenecks in biotechnology and evolutionary studies." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
