[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000360
name: Statistic
def: "A numerical summary or descriptive measure derived from data that characterizes properties of the sample or population. Statistics are essential tools for data analysis, hypothesis testing, and inference in empirical scientific research." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000146
