property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000361
name: Difference
def: "The arithmetic result of subtracting one value from another, quantifying the magnitude of change or contrast between two measurements. Differences are fundamental for assessing treatment effects, temporal trends, and comparative analysis across conditions." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
