property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000362
name: Standard deviation
def: "A measure of data dispersion quantifying how individual values deviate from the mean, expressed in the same units as the original data. Standard deviation is essential for assessing measurement variability and comparing precision across different datasets and methods." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
