[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000363
name: Standard error
def: "The standard deviation of the sampling distribution of a statistic, quantifying uncertainty in sample-based estimates. Standard error is critical for confidence intervals and hypothesis testing in statistical inference." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
