[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000364
name: Median
def: "The central value in a distribution that divides the data into equal halves when ranked in order. The median is a robust measure of central tendency less affected by outliers than the mean." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000153
