property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000365
name: Log ratio
def: "The logarithmic transformation of the ratio between two values, widely used for data visualization and statistical analysis of fold-changes and relative abundances. Log ratios stabilize variance and linearize exponential relationships in biological data." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000155
