property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000367
name: T score
def: "A statistical test value derived from t-tests used to compare means between groups and assess significance of differences. T-scores quantify the ratio of difference to variability and are fundamental for parametric hypothesis testing." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000157
