property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000368
name: Frequency
def: "The number of occurrences or repetitions of an event or observation within a defined interval or dataset. Frequency is fundamental for describing the distribution of categorical and quantitative variables in statistical analysis." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000158
