property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000369
name: Fold enrichment
def: "A ratio measure comparing the observed frequency or concentration of a feature relative to its expected or baseline value. Fold enrichment quantifies whether an outcome is more or less common than would be expected by chance." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000159
