property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000370
name: Confidence
def: "A measure of certainty or trust in an estimate, prediction, or result, often expressed as a confidence level or confidence interval. Confidence reflects the degree of reliability in statistical inference and data interpretation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
