property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000371
name: Precision
def: "The proportion of predicted positive cases that are actually true positive, measuring the exactness and reliability of predictions. High precision indicates low false positive rate in classification tasks." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000162
