property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000372
name: Recall
def: "The proportion of actual positive cases that are correctly identified by a prediction model, also known as sensitivity or true positive rate. High recall indicates comprehensive detection of true positive cases." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000163
is_a: bervo:BERVO_8000244 ! Quantitative value
