[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000377
name: Correlation
def: "A statistical measure of the strength and direction of the linear relationship between two continuous variables. Correlation values range from -1 to +1 and are essential for understanding variable associations." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
