[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000379
name: Spearman coefficient
def: "A non-parametric rank-based correlation coefficient measuring monotonic relationships between two variables without assuming normality. Spearman correlation is robust to outliers and applicable to ordinal data." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
