property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000380
name: Kendall tau coefficient
def: "A non-parametric rank correlation coefficient measuring the strength of association between two variables based on concordant and discordant pairs. Kendall tau is distribution-free and suitable for small sample sizes." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
