property_value: bervo:BERVO_Qualifier http://www.w3.org/2002/07/NA

[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000382
name: Factor
def: "A categorical variable or grouping variable that divides data into different levels or groups for analysis. Factors are essential for stratification, blocking, and categorical analysis in experimental design." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000175
