[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000383
name: Factor loading
def: "The correlation or weight indicating the contribution of an observed variable to a latent factor in factor analysis. Factor loadings quantify the relationship between variables and underlying factors." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
xref: COMO:0000176
