[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000387
name: Strand
def: "The complementary DNA strand designated as plus (5' to 3') or minus (3' to 5'), indicating directional orientation of genetic sequence. DNA strand designation is critical for sequence annotation and interpretation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
