[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000389
name: Time zone
def: "A geographic region observing a uniform standard time, defined relative to Coordinated Universal Time (UTC). Time zones are essential for accurate temporal annotation in geographically distributed studies." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
