[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000390
name: Description
def: "A text narrative providing explanatory details about an object, process, or observation. Descriptions document context, methods, and characteristics necessary for interpretation and reproducibility." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
