[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000392
name: Experimental process
def: "The category of methodology employed to generate data, including sequencing, spectroscopy, cultivation, or measurement techniques. Experimental process classification enables assessment of method-specific biases and comparability." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
