[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000393
name: Campaign
def: "A coordinated series of observations, measurements, or activities conducted over a defined temporal or spatial scope. Campaigns organize related data collection efforts for a specific research objective." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
