[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000394
name: Location
def: "A geographic point or area where observations, measurements, or samples are collected or sourced. Location information is essential for spatial analysis and environmental characterization." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
