[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000395
name: Latitude
def: "The angular distance north or south of the equator measured in degrees, minutes, and seconds (or decimal degrees). Latitude specifies the north-south coordinate in geographic positioning systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
