[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000397
name: Continent
def: "One of the major landmasses on Earth (Africa, Antarctica, Asia, Europe, North America, Oceania, South America). Continent designation provides high-level geographic classification for spatial analysis." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
