[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000398
name: Country
def: "A distinct political entity with recognized international sovereignty and defined geographic boundaries. Country classification is fundamental for regulatory, ecological, and socioeconomic stratification." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
