[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000399
name: Biome
def: "A large-scale ecosystem characterized by distinctive climate, vegetation, fauna, and biogeochemical processes. Biome classification provides context for understanding local environmental conditions and biodiversity patterns." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
