[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000400
name: Environmental feature
def: "A physical characteristic or phenomenon of the natural environment such as elevation, water body, or soil type. Environmental features influence ecosystem function and species distributions." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
