[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000401
name: Strain change type
def: "The classification of observed change in microbial strain properties including phenotypic, genotypic, or virulence changes. Strain change documentation tracks microbial evolution and adaptation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
