[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000402
name: Environmental material
def: "The physical substrate or substance collected from the environment for analysis such as soil, water, sediment, or air. Environmental material characterization specifies the source compartment of measured variables." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
