[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000403
name: Community
def: "An assemblage of populations of different species living and interacting within a defined spatial area. Community composition reflects species diversity, abundance, and ecological interactions." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
