[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000404
name: Community type
def: "The classification of communities based on dominant species, structure, or environmental characteristics. Community types enable comparative analysis across ecosystems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
