[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000472
name: Growth stage
def: "A discrete phase in the developmental progression of an organism from birth or germination through maturation and senescence. Growth stage classification enables temporal comparison of developmental processes." []
comment: Definition source - Claude 4.5 Sonnet through Claude Code in VSCode (Dec 16 2025)
