id: bervo:BERVO_8000481
name: Flagellar arrangement
def: "The spatial configuration of flagella on a bacterial cell such as monotrichous, lophotrichous, amphitrichous, or peritrichous. Flagellar arrangement is a morphological characteristic used for bacterial identification." []
