[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000532
name: Current
def: "The instantaneous or present-time value of a quantity, representing the state at the current computational time step or measurement instance. This temporal qualifier distinguishes real-time measurements from historical or predicted values in dynamic environmental models." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
