[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000533
name: Previous
def: "The value of a quantity from the preceding time step or measurement period, used for tracking temporal changes and calculating rates of change. This temporal qualifier enables analysis of how variables evolve over time in dynamic environmental simulations." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
