[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000534
name: Cumulative
def: "The accumulated or aggregated value of a quantity over a defined time period, representing the running total from a starting point to the present. This temporal qualifier is essential for quantifying total inputs, outputs, or transformations in ecosystem budgets and biogeochemical cycles." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
