[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000535
name: Logarithmic
def: "A mathematical transformation where values are expressed on a logarithmic scale, often used to compress large ranges of values or represent multiplicative relationships. This qualifier indicates that the variable has been log-transformed for analysis or presentation." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
