[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000536
name: Hydrological
def: "Relating to water movement, distribution, and properties in environmental systems including precipitation, runoff, infiltration, and groundwater flow. This qualifier indicates that a variable pertains specifically to water cycle processes and hydrological phenomena." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
