[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000538
name: Emission
def: "The release or discharge of substances, energy, or radiation from a source into the environment. This attribute quantifies outputs from biological, chemical, or physical processes including greenhouse gas emissions, pollutant releases, and radiation outputs in environmental systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
