[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000539
name: Respiration
def: "The metabolic process by which organisms convert organic compounds into energy while releasing carbon dioxide. This attribute measures the rate or amount of respiratory activity in plants, animals, and microorganisms, representing a fundamental component of ecosystem carbon cycling." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
