[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000540
name: Resistance
def: "The opposition to flow, movement, or change in a system, including electrical resistance, hydraulic resistance, or ecological resistance to disturbance. This attribute quantifies how strongly a system impedes processes or maintains stability against perturbations." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
