[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000541
name: Loss
def: "The decrease or removal of mass, energy, or substances from a system through various pathways including leaching, volatilization, runoff, or consumption. This attribute quantifies outputs and depletions in ecosystem mass balance and biogeochemical cycling." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
