[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000544
name: Capacity
def: "The maximum amount or extent that a system can hold, process, or produce, including water holding capacity, nutrient retention capacity, or productive capacity. This attribute quantifies the limits and potentials of environmental and biological systems." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
