[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000545
name: Amendment
def: "The addition of materials to soil or water to improve properties, fertility, or quality, including fertilizers, lime, compost, or other soil conditioners. This attribute quantifies the application or incorporation of amendments in managed ecosystems." []
