[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000548
name: Production
def: "The generation or creation of biomass, offspring, or products by organisms or ecosystems, including net primary production, secondary production, and reproductive output. This attribute measures the rate of biological production processes." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
