[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000549
name: Transmission
def: "The passage or transfer of energy, radiation, or substances through a medium, including light transmission through canopies or water transmission through soils. This attribute quantifies the fraction or rate of transmitted quantities through materials or systems." []
