[Term]
id: bervo:BERVO_8000550
name: Water flux
def: "The rate of water movement or transfer through a system, including evapotranspiration flux, infiltration flux, or lateral water flow. This attribute quantifies water transport processes fundamental to hydrological cycling and ecosystem water balance." []
comment: Definition source - Claude Sonnet 4 through GitHub Copilot in VSCode (Jan 8 2026)
